api_data.heading: ZS - Pfizer RFP
api_data.title_text:
Interactive Story Telling Capabilities is based on 3 major pillars - 

1) Basic & advanced charts & its layout

2) Interactivity between Charts

3) Integration with DSS & Ease of creation 

Subsequent sections in this webpage helps you walk through different types of charts and layouts along with interactivity.

PS: Visualizations are created using dummy data
